Author: nosleeptill8
Text: Oh, at work, I got ‘oh it would be nice to be naturally skinny’  In me head: *Bitch please, I work out 8x a week, obsess over my diet, don’t eat meat, dairy, alcohol, minimise processed sugars and count every fucking calorie. This ain’t natural. *  Out loud: ‘Haha, yeah, lucky me’
